question: What is the rank of the Indian Institute of Technology Bombay among Indian Universities according to the Times Higher Education’s (THE) Emerging Economies University Rankings 2020?
explanation: Indian Institute of Technology Bombay ranked third among Indian Universities according to Times Higher Education’s (THE) Emerging Economies University Rankings 2020. The world ranking of IIT Bombay is 34th. Indian Institute of Science, Bengaluru ranked first in India. The list is topped by Tsinghua University (China) among the universities in the World.
